reviewText:
I purchased for my 9 year old daughter who takes ballet.
She and her friends painted their faces and danced in the grass skirt.  Very informative and educational.  I even watched the video. A+
This was more than we had expected!  The children learned the steps so FAST and want to watch it over and over again and DANCE while watching!  Couch potatoes NO MORE!  THANK YOU!
